Jezierce  (German Haack) is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Zalewo, within Iława County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  south-west of Zalewo,  north of Iława, and  west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
